---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageCtaStrip from "../components/PageCtaStrip.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Carlsbad Fix It | Handyman in Carlsbad, CA"
  description="Contact Carlsbad Fix It for local handyman services in Carlsbad and nearby North County San Diego. Share your project details, timing, and photos to receive a clear, no-obligation estimate."
>
  <div class="bg-cf-page pt-8 pb-16 md:pt-12 md:pb-24">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 px-4 md:px-6">
      <!-- TOP GRID: INTRO + FORM -->
      <section
        class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.15fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-start"
      >
        <article class="shadow-card rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 md:p-8">
          <p class="eyebrow text-cf-textMuted">Get in touch</p>
          <h1
            class="text-h2 text-cf-text md:text-h1 mt-2 leading-snug font-semibold"
          >
            Contact Carlsbad Fix It for handyman help
          </h1>
          <p class="text-body-sm text-cf-textMuted mt-4">
            Share a short list of projects, your preferred timing, and any
            helpful photos. You will receive a reply during normal business
            hours with clear next steps and, when possible, a no-obligation
            estimate for your visit.
          </p>

          <ul class="text-cf-textMuted mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span
                class="mt-[6px] inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400"
              ></span>
              <span>
                Local handyman services for small to medium home projects in
                Carlsbad and nearby North County communities.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span
                class="mt-[6px] inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400"
              ></span>
              <span>
                Most visits group several related tasks into a single, tidy
                service window.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span
                class="mt-[6px] inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400"
              ></span>
              <span>
                Clear expectations about scope, timing, and pricing before
                anything is scheduled.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="text-cf-textMuted mt-4 text-xs">
            Messages are reviewed during normal business hours. You will usually
            receive a reply with next steps or follow-up questions before
            scheduling a visit.
          </p>
        </article>

        <section class="shadow-card rounded-3xl bg-white p-5 md:p-6">
          <p class="eyebrow text-cf-textMuted">Request an estimate</p>
          <h2 class="text-cf-text mt-1 text-base font-semibold md:text-lg">
            Share a few details about your project
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cf-textMuted mt-2 text-[13px] leading-relaxed">
            A brief description and a couple of photos (if you have them) help
            set clear expectations for what can be completed in a single visit.
          </p>

          <form
            id="contact-form"
            data-ga-lead="true"
            data-ga-form-name="Contact Form"
            data-ga-location="contact_page_main"
            action="https://formspree.io/f/mdkvzynw"
            method="POST"
            class="mt-4 space-y-3"
            data-ga-form-event="contact_form_submit"
            data-ga-label="contact_form"
          >
            <input
              type="hidden"
              name="_subject"
              value="New contact from Carlsbad Fix It contact page"
            />

            <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
              <div>
                <label
                  class="text-cf-textMuted block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase"
                >
                  Name
                </label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="name"
                  autocomplete="name"
                  placeholder="Your name"
                  class="border-cf-borderSubtle text-cf-text placeholder:text-cf-textMuted/70 focus:border-cf-accentBlue focus:ring-cf-accentBlue/15 mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label
                  class="text-cf-textMuted block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase"
                >
                  Phone
                </label>
                <input
                  type="tel"
                  name="phone"
                  autocomplete="tel"
                  placeholder="Best number to reach you"
                  class="border-cf-borderSubtle text-cf-text placeholder:text-cf-textMuted/70 focus:border-cf-accentBlue focus:ring-cf-accentBlue/15 mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none"
                />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                class="text-cf-textMuted block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase"
              >
                Email <span class="text-cf-textMuted font-normal normal-case"
                  >(optional)</span
                >
              </label>
              <input
                type="email"
                name="email"
                autocomplete="email"
                placeholder="you@example.com"
                class="border-cf-borderSubtle text-cf-text placeholder:text-cf-textMuted/70 focus:border-cf-accentBlue focus:ring-cf-accentBlue/15 mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                class="text-cf-textMuted block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase"
              >
                City
              </label>
              <input
                type="text"
                name="city"
                autocomplete="address-level2"
                placeholder="Carlsbad, CA"
                class="border-cf-borderSubtle text-cf-text placeholder:text-cf-textMuted/70 focus:border-cf-accentBlue focus:ring-cf-accentBlue/15 mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none"
              />
            </div>

            <div>
              <label
                class="text-cf-textMuted block text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase"
              >
                Project details
              </label>
              <textarea
                name="details"
                rows="4"
                placeholder="Briefly describe the work you need help with and any timing constraints."
                class="border-cf-borderSubtle text-cf-text placeholder:text-cf-textMuted/70 focus:border-cf-accentBlue focus:ring-cf-accentBlue/15 mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:outline-none"
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <button
              type="submit"
              class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFB547] to-[#FF6A3D] px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-[0_10px_25px_rgba(255,122,69,0.55)] transition hover:brightness-105 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#FF8A4A] focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-white focus:outline-none"
            >
              Submit request
            </button>
          </form>
        </section>
      </section>

      <!-- SECOND GRID: REACH US / REPLY EXPECTATIONS -->
      <section
        class="shadow-soft grid gap-6 rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:p-8"
      >
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="eyebrow text-cf-textMuted">How to reach us</p>
          <h2 class="text-cf-text text-base font-semibold md:text-lg">
            Call, text, or email about your project
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cf-textMuted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            The contact form is usually the best way to share photos and a clear
            punch list. If you prefer, you can call or text with a brief
            description and we will follow up with any details needed to
            schedule a visit.
          </p>
          <dl class="text-cf-text mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <dt class="text-cf-textMuted w-16 shrink-0">Phone</dt>
              <dd>(808) 226-6681</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <dt class="text-cf-textMuted w-16 shrink-0">Email</dt>
              <dd>carlsbadfixit@gmail.com</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="eyebrow text-cf-textMuted">When we typically reply</p>
          <h2 class="text-cf-text text-base font-semibold md:text-lg">
            What to expect after you reach out
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cf-textMuted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Messages are answered during normal business hours on weekdays. If
            you reach out in the evening or on a weekend, you will usually
            receive a reply the next business day.
          </p>
          <p class="text-cf-textMuted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            For urgent safety issues such as active leaks, electrical burning
            smells, or similar emergencies, contact the appropriate licensed
            trade contractor or emergency services before scheduling a handyman
            visit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
      <PageCtaStrip
        eyebrow="Next steps"
        title="Ready to schedule a handyman visit?"
        body="Share your punch list, preferred timing, and any helpful photos using the contact form. You will receive clear next steps and a no-obligation estimate for your home in Carlsbad, CA or a nearby North County community."
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
